data.description: Welcome to 422 Glenturret Way in Townsend, DE 19734, an exquisite home nestled in a Senior Community, offering an array of delightful features and conveniences.  As you enter through the front door, you'll immediately notice the thoughtfully designed layout. To the left, a former dining room awaits, providing an ideal space for hosting gatherings and creating cherished memories with loved ones. A hallway leads to a fully equipped kitchen, boasting stainless steel appliances, 42-inch maple cabinets, and a sophisticated granite countertop. The breakfast bar adds a touch of practicality, making casual meals a breeze.  The heart of the home is the two-story family room, which floods the space with natural light and a warm ambiance. Throughout the first floor, you'll appreciate the durable LVP flooring, flowing seamlessly into the master bedroom, creating a cohesive and stylish design.  The master bedroom offers a serene retreat with its ensuite bathroom, featuring a bathtub, stand-up shower, and a convenient double-vanity.  Moving to the second floor, you'll discover two good-sized bedrooms, providing ample space for guests or hobbies. The loft overlooking the family room offers a versatile area, perfect for a home office or a cozy reading nook.  The fully finished basement adds additional living space, offering various entertainment possibilities or creating a personalized retreat.  With a two-car garage and beautiful landscaping, this property not only offers comfort but also visual appeal.  The Senior Community is surrounded by numerous amenities, including a Golf course, community center, and a refreshing community pool, providing plenty of opportunities for leisure and recreation.  As an added benefit, the lawn is maintained by an association, ensuring a hassle-free living experience for residents.  This home is also proximal to major highways, shopping centers, and medical facilities, making daily errands and commutes a breeze.  Don't miss the chance to call 422 Glenturret Way your new home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the remarkable features and convenience this property offers in the sought-after Townsend Senior Community.
